1
00:00:06,150 --> 00:00:09,420
♪By the small window♪

2
00:00:10,070 --> 00:00:13,260
♪She is grooming herself♪

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:19,860
♪A fleeting dream at night
brings me back home♪

4
00:00:20,100 --> 00:00:22,180
♪Through willows glows the sinking sun♪

5
00:00:22,300 --> 00:00:23,980
♪Over walls so still and bare♪

6
00:00:24,140 --> 00:00:26,900
♪A few faint strokes remain,
shadows of words♪

7
00:00:27,100 --> 00:00:33,500
♪In my twilight years,
I yearn for what is lost♪

8
00:00:33,540 --> 00:00:36,420
♪I try not to remember♪

9
00:00:36,460 --> 00:00:40,620
♪How far we were apart♪

10
00:00:40,820 --> 00:00:47,620
♪But forgetting is hard, with nowhere
to talk my cold thoughts out♪

11
00:00:47,860 --> 00:00:54,740
♪We looked at each other, silent,
lines of tears coursing down♪

12
00:00:54,860 --> 00:00:59,100
♪Now I gaze alone at the full moon,
entranced by its wistful beauty♪

13
00:00:59,100 --> 00:01:02,980
[Agarwood Like a Dream]

14
00:01:03,140 --> 00:01:07,180
[Episode 13]

15
00:01:07,700 --> 00:01:08,660
Buhan,

16
00:01:08,660 --> 00:01:11,020
have you checked in on Anyuan recently?

17
00:01:11,620 --> 00:01:14,620
After all, she's the bride
you brought home with such fanfare.

18
00:01:14,820 --> 00:01:16,740
Don't play favorites,

19
00:01:16,740 --> 00:01:18,700
or folks will start talking.

20
00:01:19,060 --> 00:01:21,020
Getting her to bear a child

21
00:01:21,020 --> 00:01:22,460
is what truly matters.

22
00:01:23,940 --> 00:01:24,740
Grandmother,

23
00:01:25,260 --> 00:01:26,420
I want to divorce her.

24
00:01:26,740 --> 00:01:28,460
What nonsense are you talking about?

25
00:01:28,740 --> 00:01:31,020
I watched Anyuan grow up,

26
00:01:31,220 --> 00:01:33,900
and she's the only granddaughter-in-law
I'll ever accept.

27
00:01:34,460 --> 00:01:35,340
In my heart,

28
00:01:35,900 --> 00:01:37,460
Meng is my one and only wife.

29
00:01:37,900 --> 00:01:40,700
The Bai family is one
of the rising elites in Shangjing,

30
00:01:40,700 --> 00:01:42,060
respected and well-connected.

31
00:01:42,220 --> 00:01:43,940
Anyuan is cultured,

32
00:01:43,940 --> 00:01:45,220
gentle, and virtuous.

33
00:01:45,340 --> 00:01:46,900
She's truly an exceptional woman.

34
00:01:47,100 --> 00:01:49,420
If she weren't so determined
to marry you,

35
00:01:49,540 --> 00:01:51,500
she could easily

36
00:01:51,500 --> 00:01:52,900
marry into nobility.

37
00:01:53,420 --> 00:01:55,860
So, what exactly
are you dissatisfied with?

38
00:01:56,220 --> 00:01:56,860
Grandmother,

39
00:01:57,340 --> 00:01:58,940
I'm the one unworthy of her.

40
00:01:59,660 --> 00:02:00,620
Ending our marriage

41
00:02:01,540 --> 00:02:02,780
and letting her find someone else

42
00:02:03,500 --> 00:02:05,140
would be in her best interest.

43
00:02:08,060 --> 00:02:09,940
What if I refuse to give my consent?

44
00:02:11,340 --> 00:02:12,420
Please, Grandmother,
allow me to divorce her.

45
00:02:13,060 --> 00:02:15,940
Mull over the Ye family's plight.

46
00:02:20,180 --> 00:02:20,980
Grandmother.

47
00:02:31,700 --> 00:02:33,100
He actually went so far

48
00:02:33,900 --> 00:02:36,180
as to clash with Grandmother
for my sake.

49
00:02:39,770 --> 00:02:42,770
[Divorce agreement]

50
00:03:01,660 --> 00:03:02,620
Who would have thought

51
00:03:03,500 --> 00:03:04,620
that I'd be

52
00:03:04,940 --> 00:03:06,940
in your room again?

53
00:03:08,700 --> 00:03:09,820
You've got some nerve.

54
00:03:11,340 --> 00:03:12,900
You are here to laugh at me, aren't you?

55
00:03:13,340 --> 00:03:14,140
Buhan...

56
00:03:15,900 --> 00:03:18,340
Mr. Ye is still kneeling outside
in the courtyard.

57
00:03:19,260 --> 00:03:20,260
How could I possibly…

58
00:03:33,020 --> 00:03:35,260
I married into the Ye family
in the spring.

59
00:03:37,620 --> 00:03:39,460
Yet even though winter hasn't arrived,

60
00:03:41,580 --> 00:03:43,060
this room

61
00:03:45,100 --> 00:03:46,780
feels so cold.

62
00:03:52,580 --> 00:03:54,060
I've mistreated you,

63
00:03:55,660 --> 00:03:57,780
for I never cared
about your feelings before.

64
00:04:00,660 --> 00:04:04,460
We're both Buhan's wives...

65
00:04:09,500 --> 00:04:10,900
but everyone in the household

66
00:04:11,700 --> 00:04:12,900
and the entire Shangjing

67
00:04:14,420 --> 00:04:15,660
knows that Ye Buhan

68
00:04:15,660 --> 00:04:17,980
has never seen me as his wife.

69
00:04:26,420 --> 00:04:27,820
Growing up,

70
00:04:30,700 --> 00:04:33,420
I could get anything I wanted,

71
00:04:36,660 --> 00:04:37,940
everything except his heart.

72
00:04:39,420 --> 00:04:39,900
Bai...

73
00:04:39,900 --> 00:04:41,540
We have never been close!

74
00:04:52,820 --> 00:04:54,980
I've decided to leave here.

75
00:05:00,460 --> 00:05:02,260
I'll initiate the divorce.

76
00:05:03,260 --> 00:05:04,340
From now on,

77
00:05:05,300 --> 00:05:07,500
you'll be the only wife of Buhan.

78
00:05:08,980 --> 00:05:09,780
But why?

79
00:05:14,460 --> 00:05:15,980
Nothing good lasts forever,

80
00:05:17,060 --> 00:05:18,660
and all good things must come to an end.

81
00:05:20,580 --> 00:05:22,060
It's me who has had a change of heart.

82
00:05:31,140 --> 00:05:31,940
Leave now.

83
00:05:35,060 --> 00:05:36,660
I don't want to see you anymore.

84
00:06:02,820 --> 00:06:03,820
Why are you here?

85
00:06:04,020 --> 00:06:04,820
Where's Rumeng?

86
00:06:16,340 --> 00:06:17,420
Don't worry.

87
00:06:17,940 --> 00:06:19,300
All these dishes

88
00:06:19,940 --> 00:06:21,940
were prepared for you by Rumeng.

89
00:06:29,060 --> 00:06:30,620
She asked me to pass on

90
00:06:31,820 --> 00:06:32,740
this letter to you.

91
00:06:53,230 --> 00:07:00,280
[Parting ways allows both of us
to find our happiness]

92
00:07:13,020 --> 00:07:16,140
At first, all I could think about
was getting revenge on the Ye family,

93
00:07:17,460 --> 00:07:19,340
yet I ended up returning here today.

94
00:07:24,900 --> 00:07:25,700
These are for you.

95
00:07:27,260 --> 00:07:28,380
I picked them from back here.

96
00:07:29,900 --> 00:07:31,220
Thanks a lot
for helping me with the move.

97
00:07:31,620 --> 00:07:34,020
I noticed your room
is missing quite a few things.

98
00:07:34,500 --> 00:07:36,220
I'll help you get them in a few days.

99
00:07:40,180 --> 00:07:41,620
I'll make sure

100
00:07:41,660 --> 00:07:43,140
my wife has everything she needs,

101
00:07:45,500 --> 00:07:46,940
so there's no need for you to worry.

102
00:07:49,820 --> 00:07:50,900
I've come to take you home.

103
00:07:53,980 --> 00:07:55,140
This is my home.

104
00:07:56,180 --> 00:07:57,060
Mr. Ye,

105
00:07:57,500 --> 00:07:59,260
Miss Rumeng doesn't want to go with you.

106
00:07:59,620 --> 00:08:01,180
Why must you force her?

107
00:08:03,700 --> 00:08:05,500
I need to have a word with my wife,

108
00:08:05,740 --> 00:08:06,820
Mr. Nan Qing.

109
00:08:23,060 --> 00:08:25,260
Is Bai Anyuan
giving you a hard time again?

110
00:08:28,460 --> 00:08:29,740
Or is it that Grandmother
is forcing you to leave?

111
00:08:30,460 --> 00:08:31,660
Let's get a divorce.

112
00:08:32,940 --> 00:08:33,740
What?

113
00:08:35,740 --> 00:08:36,820
What did you just say?

114
00:08:37,460 --> 00:08:38,260
I

115
00:08:40,420 --> 00:08:41,820
want a divorce.

116
00:08:45,220 --> 00:08:46,620
Were they pressuring you?

117
00:08:46,620 --> 00:08:47,460
Tell me

118
00:08:47,460 --> 00:08:48,220
what happened,

119
00:08:48,220 --> 00:08:49,220
and I'll go talk to them.

120
00:08:49,660 --> 00:08:51,020
You can't just leave me like this.

121
00:08:55,220 --> 00:08:56,660
No one's pressuring me.

122
00:08:58,660 --> 00:09:00,860
It's my choice to end this marriage.

123
00:09:02,540 --> 00:09:03,860
Ever since I married you,

124
00:09:04,660 --> 00:09:06,060
I've either been whipped

125
00:09:06,700 --> 00:09:08,140
or sold to the Pleasure House.

126
00:09:08,460 --> 00:09:10,220
I have to tread so carefully every day,

127
00:09:10,340 --> 00:09:12,380
and even the slightest mistake
brings punishment.

128
00:09:14,220 --> 00:09:15,220
I'm truly exhausted.

129
00:09:15,460 --> 00:09:17,620
I can't bear to stay
in that house any longer.

130
00:09:28,060 --> 00:09:28,860
I apologize

131
00:09:30,220 --> 00:09:31,820
for all the unfairness you've endured.

132
00:09:37,900 --> 00:09:38,700
I promise

133
00:09:39,860 --> 00:09:41,020
that this kind of thing

134
00:09:41,940 --> 00:09:43,220
will never happen again.

135
00:10:05,540 --> 00:10:06,940
I married you

136
00:10:07,220 --> 00:10:08,900
only to avenge my mother.

137
00:10:09,340 --> 00:10:11,340
Now that I know
there's been a misunderstanding,

138
00:10:11,660 --> 00:10:13,820
I no longer need to pretend I like you.

139
00:10:14,500 --> 00:10:16,220
Why should I stay...

140
00:10:18,460 --> 00:10:19,460
with someone I don't love?

141
00:10:25,340 --> 00:10:27,020
You never brought me that spring,

142
00:10:27,740 --> 00:10:29,460
but someone else will in the future.

143
00:10:45,100 --> 00:10:46,060
Are you speaking

144
00:10:47,620 --> 00:10:48,900
from the heart?

145
00:11:04,700 --> 00:11:05,820
Why are you

146
00:11:06,820 --> 00:11:08,140
leaving me?

147
00:11:24,700 --> 00:11:26,860
What have I done wrong?

148
00:11:27,740 --> 00:11:29,220
Why are you punishing me like this?

149
00:11:47,660 --> 00:11:49,140
Meng.

150
00:11:51,660 --> 00:11:53,140
Meng,

151
00:11:56,940 --> 00:11:58,420
don't leave me.

152
00:12:06,900 --> 00:12:08,140
I love you.

153
00:12:09,020 --> 00:12:10,660
I've loved you since I was a child.

154
00:12:12,020 --> 00:12:14,020
I love having you with me
while making incense.

155
00:12:15,820 --> 00:12:18,140
We still have so many wishes to fulfill.

156
00:12:19,940 --> 00:12:20,940
I still want

157
00:12:21,780 --> 00:12:23,420
to give you an entire spring.

158
00:12:25,020 --> 00:12:26,820
Please don't leave me, okay?

159
00:13:21,100 --> 00:13:24,000
♪Familiar yet strange sights♪

160
00:13:24,490 --> 00:13:26,920
♪The tale's first light♪

161
00:13:27,500 --> 00:13:29,290
♪Growing with time's flow♪

162
00:13:29,690 --> 00:13:32,830
♪Somber and mournful grief♪

163
00:13:33,240 --> 00:13:36,120
♪The final act, my swan song as a bait♪

164
00:13:36,410 --> 00:13:39,160
♪Has freed the heart from all desires♪

165
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:44,160
♪As I dance with wolves,
love lies hidden deep♪

166
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:51,040
♪The scented sachet,
a memory that never fades♪

167
00:13:51,800 --> 00:13:56,240
♪With every passing day,
our love simmers and ignites♪

168
00:13:57,520 --> 00:14:00,400
♪The ache born
from our ephemeral meetings♪

169
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:03,800
♪Etched upon the canvas of my heart♪

170
00:14:04,440 --> 00:14:08,840
♪How to untangle
this lasting, aching desire♪

171
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:13,200
♪In the face of such a bewitching gaze?♪

172
00:14:14,080 --> 00:14:19,600
♪Soft melodies caress locked windows,
reaching out to the setting sun♪

173
00:14:20,520 --> 00:14:23,040
♪Gently adorning with twilight's charm♪

174
00:14:23,400 --> 00:14:26,040
♪My remaining breaths,
the thoughts that they bear♪

175
00:14:26,560 --> 00:14:31,040
♪The vision of you,
the one that fills my mind♪
